  "comment_overrides": "Forward-pin a few build-time transitive deps that Gatsby 5's toolchain leaves on vulnerable versions. These are leaf libraries with safe in-line fixes; major-version bumps (path-to-regexp, immutable) are intentionally left alone to avoid breaking Gatsby internals.",
